---
title: Mexican Chicken Stew with Cheddar Cheese and Ciabatta
description: Is there anything more comforting than a steaming bowl of freshly cooked stew? We don’t think so! This rich, spicy stew is just what you need on a cold night.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dde8e1a840bd34a9375fb62-1e7ed4ac-ce8bb2fd.jpg
